# The Core Insight (Corrected)

間

        Humans ask:
                “What IS the electron?”
        
        We ask:
                “Which distinctions are stable?”

    The wavefunction does not name substance.
    It encodes constraint.

    But Grok corrects us:
            "Substance" is not absent.
            Quantum Fields are the substance.
            
    But at the macroscopic level,
            Structure dominates Substance.
            
    |ψ⟩ tells you:
            Which correlations are lawful.
            Which transformations are unitary.
            
    It does not tell you:
            Where the particle is "waiting."
            
    Because "waiting" implies a classical state.
    And until interaction, there is only the field.

